description: A walking tour of Woodside near Croydon

events.name: Drop in
events.notes: Please let us know if you plan to visit. Doing so allows the venue to plan ahead and you will be notified by email about any changes to the programme that might affect your visit.

factsheet.heading: Woodside walking tour
paragraphs: This walking tour of Woodside starting at 2.30pm on Thursday 14th September 2023 at St Luke's Church Woodside will also include the site of Ashburton Convent; Woodside Fire Station; some very early Croydon Corporation housing; Woodside Green; and Woodside War Memorial.

location.address: St Luke's Church, Woodside, Portland Road, Croydon, SE25 4RB
travel_info:
Additional travel info: The bus routes are 312 and 197 to the top of Portland Road for St. Luke's Church.
Woodside tram stop is nearby.

name: Woodside walking tour
